THE Advertisers’ Association of Nigeria (ADVAN) is set to hold its annual Awards for Marketing Excellence from on Sunday, 17th of November in Lagos. A statement signed by the Executive Secretary, Ediri Ose-Ediale said winners of the Awards for Marketing Excellence will now be showcased in the directory of all World Federation of Advertisers’ (WFA) member companies. The statement said another development is that entries for the awards will now be assessed by both local and international assessors. The  event which is set to highlight the “Business Value of Creativity” will witness local and international professionals sharing insights on the theme of the day, the statement further said the Awards’ offer the ultimate platform for improving brand awareness and loyalty, by increasing the respective recipients’ prestige.” The ADVAN Awards winners are acknowledged as industry leaders and named the elite in their industry, the statement said.  